This socket head cap screw has a length of 300mm with a threading of M16 * 2mm [Partially Threaded]. It is made of Black-Oxide Alloy Steel, providing a mild resistance to corrosion in dry environments.

ISO Metric Pitch | Coarse threads are an industry standard. These screws are classified as DIN 912 and comply with dimensional standards.
